-- MOVES-Boston Private Bank promotes Donahue to commercial loan officer 
-- 
-- Fri Aug 08, 2014 04:00PM EDT
-- None



Aug 8 (Reuters) - Boston Private Bank and Trust Co [BPFHT.UL], a wealth management and private banking company, promoted David Donahue to commercial loan officer.

Donahue, to be based in the company's headquarters in Boston, is currently senior credit analyst. The company said Donahue will oversee financing for privately held middle-market companies.